{{Infobox dungeon |name = Pokémon Village |image = [[File:Pokémon Village.png|250px]] |caption = A map of Pokémon Village. |tokens = 725,000 |location = East of Route 20. }} '''Pokémon Village''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Kalos]]. It initially has 100 tiles arranged in a 10x10 square, including 10 chest tiles, 23 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
